        '\n' +
        'import "@openzeppelin/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol";\n' +
        'import "@openzeppelin/contracts/token/ERC20/extensions/ERC20Burnable.sol";\n' +

        'contract ViCOIN is ERC20, ERC20Burnable, Ownable {\n' +
        '    constructor() ERC20("ViCOIN", "ViC") {\n' +
        '        _mint(msg.sender, 2000 * 10 ** decimals());\n' +
        '    }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '    function mint(address to, uint256 amount) public onlyOwner {\n' +
        '        _mint(to, amount);\n' +
        '    }\n' +
